# Exam Prep That Delivers ResultsHistory
## Practice questions, AI feedback, and notes to make exam prep stress-free.
[Start studying — It's free](https://studydojo.com/</signup>)
## 
Studying is hard, we make it easy.
## Learn new concepts with notes or flashcards
    * Explore a rich library of notes for all subjects.
    * Convert your notes into flashcards for quick revision.
    * Enhance your learning with Jojo AI at every step.


![Learn new concepts with notes or flashcards](https://studydojo.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flanding%2Ffeature-grid-3.jpg&w=1080&q=75)
## Revise with thousands of practice questions
    * Choose from thousands of exam-style questions
    * Select your preferred question type (MCQs, short answer, etc.)
    * Filter by difficulty level, topic, and more...


![Revise with thousands of practice questions](https://studydojo.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flanding%2Ffeature-grid-1.jpg&w=1080&q=75)
## Instant feedback and grading with Jojo AI
    * See how you score against the markscheme
    * Identifies your strengths and weaknesses.
    * Lists out strategies for improving your responses.


![Instant feedback and grading with Jojo AI](https://studydojo.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flanding%2Ffeature-grid-2.jpg&w=1080&q=75)
## Generate mock papers for exam preparation
    * Filter based on topical questions
    * Print or download your mock paper
    * Get instant feedback on your answers


![Generate mock papers for exam preparation](https://studydojo.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flanding%2Ffeature-grid-4.jpg&w=1080&q=75)
## Studying is hard, we make it easy. and here's how...
Learn mode
### Learn with interactive lessons
Speed through your curriculum with bite-sized lessons. Jump between flashcards, matching answers, and fill in the blanks. Short, sweet, and fun. 
[Start learning - it's free](https://studydojo.com/</signup>)

Study notes & Flashcards
### Review concepts with expert notes
Access thousands of expert curated study notes and flashcards tailored to your curriculum. Finally, notes you understand and flashcards you can trust.
[Start learning - it's free](https://studydojo.com/</signup>)
Your browser does not support the video tag.
Questionbank
### Grind with exam-style questions
Practice with 100% free exam style questions specific to your curriculum. Keep track of all your progress and get instant feedback on your answers with mark schemes and Jojo AI. 
[Start learning - it's free](https://studydojo.com/</signup>)

Exam mode
### Test your knowledge with mock exams
Drill down on your weaknesses or key areas by building your own mock exams. Time yourself to experience exam conditions so you're never caught off guard.
